column49: I really enjoyed taking this course and I felt that the online forum gave me a chance to personally consider my beliefs around a certain situation, and how I would ethically react before discussing it with my classmates.
column51: I agree completely! It was such a structured class that you knew exactly what had to be completed when and there was no room to slack off and so I learned as much as I have in other face to face classes.

column83: I really enjoyed going through the voice threads alone and forming my own opinion on the various topics before hearing the opinions of others. I felt it let me form a more authentic belief.
column84: I dislike the length of the synchronous meeting and the fact it was only once a week. I feel it may have been more beneficial to break it into 2 meeting.
column85: To stay on top of their work and make sure to have a schedule because when you dont physically have to go to class it is easy to forget when things are due.
